# Shopify Webhook Test Kit — environment template.
# Copy to `.env` and fill in your real value. NEVER commit a real secret.
# The kit reads the NAME of this variable from the environment and never
# stores, logs, or echoes the value.

# Your Shopify app's WEBHOOK SIGNING SECRET.
#   - For webhooks created via the Admin API / your app config, this is your
#     app's CLIENT SECRET (Partners dashboard -> your app -> Client credentials
#     -> "Client secret" / "API secret key").
#   - For webhooks created manually in the Shopify admin (Settings ->
#     Notifications -> Webhooks), it is the shared secret shown on that page.
#   This is NOT the Admin API access token (shpat_/shpca_) and NOT the API key.
#   It is the secret Shopify uses to compute X-Shopify-Hmac-Sha256.
SHOPIFY_WEBHOOK_SECRET=replace-with-your-webhook-signing-secret
